message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with sound and audio processing. Other likely categories could be cs.CL (Computation and Language) as the paper deals with speech enhancement, cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the paper uses neural network models, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as the paper deals with image processing, and cs.MM (Multimedia) as the paper deals with audio and music processing.
